  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971540/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765177588\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971540/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765177588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/971540/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765177588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The Hermes-2700 spaceship, driven by a fearless pilot, Che goes in search of the planets for the life-giving civilization SAMS, Che's home planet was not suitable for life after the attack of the cruel empire “Pured”<br><br>In Sams, you will have to control a spacecraft to destroy enemies, you can play alone or together with friends on one computer.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 6 unique planets<br></li><li> Single player game<br></li><li> cooperative mode<br></li><li> support for two keyboards or two gamepads</li></ul>",
